    "One should act with a similarity transformation on these operators to translate to our conventions for the N = 4 topological algebra generators.",
    "However, this similarity transformation will have a trivial effect in terms of identifying which terms in the correlation function are non-vanishing.",
    "Since the Ψ A,j r and ∂X j n have non-trivial ghost contributions, they will change which terms contribute to the measure for non-vanishing correlation functions.",
    "We are yet to fully understand the contributions from ∂X j n, since these have a non-trivial commutator with G-C.",
    "It therefore cannot be deduced so simply that any insertions of e -ρ-iσ-iH 1 ∂ X2 or e -ρ-iσ-iH 2 ∂ X1 will vanish."
